      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. ZAIDEN (1) filled the minor placings again last time when second (20.20) at this track, making it three straight minors on end. Strike rate this distance strong having won three of six tries. Looks a key player drawing the cherry. FERNLEY GIRL (4) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Panther's Way (20.27) in a Grade 5 H. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to feature. DR. ODIN (2) has missed the frame at last two runs but could not have been more impressive the run prior in his solid 28.86 win at Sale over 510m. Must include on winning run three back. YOU FOUND ME (3) is another with top-three prospects.",
